OL,5, Fans are asking US singer Lizzo to     
OL,6, delete and re-record her new single,   
OL,7, Grrrls, to remove an ableist slur from 
OL,8, the lyrics.                            
OL,10,FThe song was released on Friday 10     
OL,11,FJune, and almost immediately received  
OL,12,Fcriticism from disability advocates.   
OL,14,FLizzo prominently uses a derogatory    
OL,15,Fterm for cerebral palsy, also known as 
OL,16,Fspastic diplegia, in the first verse.  
OL,18,F"It's absolutely shocking, It really   
OL,19,Fmade me flinch," says talent agent     
OL,20,FAbbie Hills, who has cerebral palsy.   
